Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Griffith Observatory
Description: Griffith Observatory is one of the most popular historical landmarks in Los Angeles!

Name: Apple Park
Description: Apple Park is the corporate headquarters of Apple Inc., and people who are interested in the products can visit Apple Park Visitor Center in Apple Park.

Name: Yellowstone National Park
Description: Yellowstone National Park is one of the largest national parks that has the most active, diverse, and intact collections of combined geothermal features.

Name: Walt Disney World
Description: Walt Disney World is the largest Disney theme park in the world which brings people happiness. It is also known as “the most magical place on earth”.

Name: Times Square
Description: Times Square is one of the most famous places where people celebrate the New Year's Eve.
